{"tid":231351,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"俾新搬嚟嘅鄰居當變態佬，相當難受","createTime":"2017-05-06T03:42:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-06T09:31:21.000Z","uid":5077,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bf4a6ff424598fc973f58a864a62762d9810caf9","tid":231351,"uid":5077,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T03:42:03.000Z","msg":"今日我隔離個單位有對新婚夫婦入伙，<br />\n咁禮貌上我都要送啲嘢過去恭喜佢地啦，<br />\n我就特登落街揀咗個果籃，<br />\n㩒佢地鐘仔打算送俾佢地，<br />\n佢地一開門好似有啲愕然咁，<br />\n但都有照開門俾我入去，<br />\n我見到個人妻淨係著件背心咁行嚟行去，<br />\n我梗係會望住佢驚佢凍親啦，<br />\n佢老公就當正我癲佬咁係咁攬實佢老婆，<br />\n我仲以為有咩咁好攬，我又攬落去試吓，<br />\n點知係撚頂中咗個人妻屎忽，佢就叫咗出嚟，<br />\n見佢面紅紅咁望住佢老公，<br />\n我都知呢個係signal嚟，咁我就除褲唔客氣啦"},{"pid":"27dc3d01113bcba3d50be434a404a11655fa32fd","tid":231351,"uid":41974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T03:45:40.000Z","msg":"創意臺"},{"pid":"1c349b3ac5c4019beb8838d5fe2ad2858413c7b8","tid":231351,"uid":82398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T03:48:06.000Z","msg":"唔好咁多幻想啦"},{"pid":"585ddb119e2b7c91fa01359e2437379b4630157c","tid":231351,"uid":84998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T03:54:08.000Z","msg":"有病就睇醫生"},{"pid":"0c6a4789c650b79633dd75697213d5bc48ed6782","tid":231351,"uid":86893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T04:01:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d71dd79a788fac2d888cd554b5167348e9596e5","tid":231351,"uid":33206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T04:03:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">◉‿◉</span></span>"},{"pid":"014e896cf006b5917e430b42266fc765776e898e","tid":231351,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T04:27:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">◉‿◉</span></span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"707e7fb1f3fe41595c6a0dc1546103e1e687c654","tid":231351,